column5: Hey, just wanted to say hello, been lurking for a year or two i guess. I have always enjoyed the reports, so heres a few pics or my own.
Looking forward to some reports from you!!!
Ah yes ... another one comes out.   Welcome to the board and don't be a stranger.
....Good morning, nice to have you on board.
Hello 12footspringbok, welcome to OFC  Nice pics and good mix bag of them Looking forward to your futur reports. Leechman
Welcome aboard! Nice fish. Keep the pictures coming. We love pictures!
Welcome to the Dark side.  Its nice when there are converters. Where they can interact with the rest.
